lead_paragraph: Clint Dempsey, Kyle Beckerman, Chris Wondolowski, Graham Zusi and Brad Evans were among the veteran players left off Jurgen Klinsmann's training camp roster ahead of exhibition games against Iceland and Canada.

headline.main: Dempsey, Beckerman Left Off Youthful US Soccer Roster
